            <sentence>
                <offset>0</offset>
                <text>﻿A 16-month-old female patient was admitted to our clinic with a complaint of short stature.</text>
                <annotation id="1">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0004322</infon>
                    <location length="13" offset="78"/>
                    <text>short stature</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>93</offset>
                <text>Her case history revealed that she was born as the first child of her consanguineous parents.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>187</offset>
                <text>The patient was born on the 39th week of gestation with a birth weight of 1740 grams and birth length of 42 cm.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>299</offset>
                <text>There is no known prior case of hereditary disease in her family.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>365</offset>
                <text>On physical examination, the patient’s length was 67 cm [-3.6 standard deviation (SD) score], her body weight was 7.2 kg (-2.9 SD score), and head circumference 42 cm (below 3rd percentile).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>556</offset>
                <text>Her features consisted of a triangular face, a fleshy nose tip, a long philtrum, a prominent mouth and lips with a pointed chin alongside, lumbar lordosis, and prominent heels.</text>
                <annotation id="2">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0000325</infon>
                    <location length="15" offset="28"/>
                    <text>triangular face</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="3">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0000414</infon>
